When talking to newly promoted cadres, it is necessary to make explicit demands on honesty and self-discipline.
It is necessary to urge the leading bodies at all levels to adhere to democratic centralism, establish rules and procedures for improving the rules and procedures, and conscientiously implement the system of combining collective leadership with individual division of labor.
