According to the request, organizations at all levels (personnel) should effectively strengthen supervision over the work of selecting and appointing party and government leading cadres.
It is necessary to further improve the supervision measures for the nomination of cadres, inspection, deliberation, and discussion of decisions, so as to provide a strong guarantee for the selection of cadres who are politically reliable, capable of working and working in a hard work style, and who have gained the trust of the masses.
It is necessary to step up inspection of the implementation of the regulations on the appointment of cadres, seriously investigate and deal with violations of the regulations on the appointment of cadres, and resolutely curb unhealthy trends and corrupt practices in the use of personnel.
